fields.Title: KIM SWITCH / DISCUSSING KLAASJE DOWNSTAIRS
fields.Description: this should blink ONLY DOWNSTAIRS and after Klaasje rape hub exit

fields.Title: You: ""You think this will make them coop..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You think this will make them cooperate?"

fields.Title: Volition: "Like hell you would have -- remembe..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Like hell you would have -- remember?

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""You think so?" A shadow runs acros..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You think so?" A shadow runs across his face. "She seemed forthcoming... Unusually so. Being forthcoming about some things is a good way to obscure other things."

fields.Title: You: ""I'm not sure she *had* to lie. I w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm not sure she *had* to lie. I wouldn't have known."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""You think so?" A shadow runs acros..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You think so?" A shadow runs across his face. "Being candid is the best way to lie. The appearance of candour, with some facts thrown in, draws attention away from whatever one chooses to omit."

fields.Title: You: ""Perhaps that's because you *are*?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Perhaps that's because you *are*?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""She seemed forthcoming to me... Un..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "She seemed forthcoming to me... Unusually so. Being forthcoming with some things is a good way to obscure other things. But I wouldn't call myself compromised..."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Anyway, we should move. I suspect..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Anyway, we should move. I suspect our investigation will bring us back soon enough."

fields.Title: You: ""Got it. Let's go." [Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: "Got it. Let's go." [Leave.]

fields.Title: Drama: "You would have caught it."
fields.Dialogue Text: You would have caught it.

fields.Title: You: "(Nod.) "I would have caught it.""
fields.Dialogue Text: (Nod.) "I would have caught it."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""So you said to her.... What did yo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "So you said to her.... What did you *mean* by it?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""What do you mean by that?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What do you mean by that?"

fields.Title: You: ""Something is off here.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Something is off here."

fields.Title: You: ""Well. I am, anyway.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Well. I am, anyway."

fields.Title: You: ""She seems candid.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "She seems candid."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""What else could she have done? Lie..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What else could she have done? Lie? She saw there was no way to lie and get away with it."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""The best liars are always forthcom..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "The best liars are always forthcoming... Anyway, we should move. I suspect our investigation will bring us back here soon enough."

fields.Title: You: "(Whisper.) "She has half my skillse..."
fields.Dialogue Text: (Whisper.) "She has half my skillset compromised, singing her tune. My assessments of her are untrustworthy."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I am not easily swayed by young wo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I am not easily swayed by young women. But on the other hand... the best liars are candid. And she was candid."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Nothing will make them respect the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Nothing will make them respect the RCM. But it will disrupt the game they prepared for us. We just stripped off one layer of whatever it is. Her decision to not corroborate their story was *definitely* not part of the plan."

fields.Title: You: "(Say in a hushed voice.) "Why *did*..."
fields.Dialogue Text: (Say in a hushed voice.) "Why *did* she tell us all of that?"

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""If not you, then me. It was a smar..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "If not you, then me. It was a smart move from her."

fields.Title: You: "(Whisper) "I know she's manipulativ..."
fields.Dialogue Text: (Whisper) "I know she's manipulative."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""She may be trying to control the p..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "She may be trying to control the pace of the investigation. Anyway, we should move. I suspect our inquiries will bring us back here soon enough."

fields.Title: You: ""I have reason to doubt my ability..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I have reason to doubt my ability to see through her lies."

fields.Title: Volition: "The lieutenant seems oddly sure he..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant seems oddly sure he is not compromised, not psychologically at least. Is it hubris?
